        "subject": "LU-0000 tests: add layout verification to EC tests",
        "message": "LU-0000 tests: add layout verification to EC tests\n\nAdd helper functions and verification code to EC tests in\nllapi_layout_test to ensure that files created with EC\nlayouts have the correct layout parameters.\n\nThree reusable helper functions were added:\n- __verify_ec_comp(): Verifies EC parameters (PARITY flag,\n  cstripe_count, dstripe_count)\n- __verify_comp_extent(): Verifies component extents\n- __verify_stripe_count(): For future stripe count\n  verification\n\nTests 50, 51, and 52 now verify the created file layouts\nby reading them back and checking component extents and EC\nparameters.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I46bbce36863dc6047eea8df9247746c8b814b6b1\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
